allowance(address,address).notice: Returns the allowance a spender has from an owner.

approve(address,uint256).notice: Approves a spender to use an amount of LP tokens.

balanceOf(address).notice: Returns the LP token balance of an owner.

burn(address).notice: Burns LP tokens to withdraw underlying assets.

getReserves().notice: Returns the reserves of the pair and the timestamp of the last block in which an interaction occurred.

price0CumulativeLast().notice: Returns the cumulative price of token0.

price1CumulativeLast().notice: Returns the cumulative price of token1.

swap(uint256,uint256,address,bytes).notice: Performs a swap directly on the pair contract.

token0().notice: Returns the address of the first token in the pair.

token1().notice: Returns the address of the second token in the pair.

totalSupply().notice: Returns the total supply of LP tokens.

transfer(address,uint256).notice: Transfers LP tokens to a recipient.

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).notice: Transfers LP tokens from a sender to a recipient using the caller's allowance.
